WEBVTT

00:00.059 --> 00:02.895
Today, more people look online to find deals for everything.

00:03.279 --> 00:05.945
From a shampoo and cut to an auto tune-up.

00:06.743 --> 00:09.323
To help you get amazing deals on the best places to eat,...

00:09.637 --> 00:11.788
...shop, play, and stay in your area,...

00:12.738 --> 00:14.479
...we've created a smart, new way to find them,...

00:15.103 --> 00:15.877
...Google Offers!

00:17.187 --> 00:20.424
We're working with thousands of local businesses and even other deal sources,...

00:20.527 --> 00:25.209
...like local experience site Gilt City, so you can find a huge collection of offers all in one place.

00:26.438 --> 00:29.869
And you can personalize your deals so you'll only receive the offers that matter to you.

00:30.195 --> 00:31.693
Just sign up with Google Offers...

00:31.790 --> 00:33.732
...and we'll send the best deals right to you.

00:34.201 --> 00:37.149
Here's how it works. Subscribe to Google Offers,...

00:37.673 --> 00:40.432
...tell us what types of offers you like, and your locations.

00:40.883 --> 00:43.233
We'll email you the best deals that match your interests.

00:44.162 --> 00:47.521
Click the "buy" button, enter the appropriate information, and you're done.

00:47.949 --> 00:52.081
Print the voucher or show it on your mobile phone to the business owner and enjoy the offer.

00:52.514 --> 00:55.259
Click the "My Offers" tab to keep track of all your vouchers.

00:56.612 --> 01:00.603
And be sure to let your friends, family, and colleagues know about Google Offers...

01:00.901 --> 01:02.496
...so they can get in on great deals, too.

01:03.186 --> 01:05.488
Join us at Google.com/offers.

